---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import "../../styles/globals.css";
import { Header } from "../../components/Header";
import InnerPageCTA from "../../components/InnerPageCTA.astro";
import Footer from "../../components/Footer.astro";

const b = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<Layout
  title="parcelLab CTO Julian Krenge Features on FUTR Podcast - parcelLab"
  description="CTO Julian Krenge discusses supply chain challenges, Operations Experience Management, and parcelLab's co-creation approach on the FUTRtech Podcast."
>
  <Header client:load />
  <main>
    <!-- Article Header -->
    <section class="section-generous">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-[1440px] px-6 md:px-12">
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-[800px]">
          <a href={`${b}/blog/`} class="group mb-8 inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-medium text-[var(--ink-muted)] transition-colors hover:text-[#3D3AD3]">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="transition-transform group-hover:-translate-x-0.5"><path d="M19 12H5"/><path d="m12 19-7-7 7-7"/></svg>
            Back to blog
          </a>
          <span class="mb-4 inline-block rounded-full bg-[#3D3AD3]/10 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-[#3D3AD3]">Company News</span>
          <h1 class="text-display text-[var(--ink)]">parcelLab CTO Julian Krenge Features on FUTR Podcast</h1>
          <div class="mt-6 flex items-center gap-4 text-sm text-[var(--ink-muted)]">
            <span>By <strong class="font-medium text-[var(--ink-secondary)]">parcelLab Team</strong></span>
            <span class="h-1 w-1 rounded-full bg-[var(--ink-muted)]"></span>
            <time datetime="2022-05-06">May 6, 2022</time>
            <span class="h-1 w-1 rounded-full bg-[var(--ink-muted)]"></span>
            <span>4 min read</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Article Body -->
    <section class="pb-16 md:pb-24">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-[800px] px-6 md:px-12">
        <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed text-lg">
          parcelLab's CTO and co-founder Julian Krenge appeared on the FUTRtech Podcast in an episode titled "Solve the Supply Chain Disaster with parcelLab." The discussion with hosts Chris Brandt and Sandesh Patel examines supply chain challenges affecting e-commerce brands and how Operations Experience Management can help.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-heading text-[var(--ink)] mt-12 mb-4">Key Takeaway 1: Customization Is Key</h2>
        <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
          E-commerce retailers increasingly differentiate themselves through tailored customer experiences. Rather than relying on third-party delivery experiences, brands should control each touchpoint to customize interactions.
        </p>

        <div class="my-10 rounded-2xl bg-[var(--surface-sunken)] p-8">
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.1em] text-[var(--ink-muted)]">CTO Perspective</p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-lg font-medium text-[var(--ink)]">"It's so obvious when you think about it -- why don't retailers leverage that part of the journey?"</p>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-[var(--ink-muted)]">-- Julian Krenge, CTO, parcelLab</p>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-heading text-[var(--ink)] mt-12 mb-4">Key Takeaway 2: Operations Experience Management Provides Untapped Data</h2>
        <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
          parcelLab's platform transforms operational data into personalized experiences while providing retailers access to previously disconnected information. Understanding regional delivery performance, customer engagement patterns, and preferred communication channels reveals valuable insights most companies overlook.
        </p>

        <div class="my-10 rounded-2xl bg-[var(--surface-sunken)] p-8">
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.1em] text-[var(--ink-muted)]">On Data</p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-lg font-medium text-[var(--ink)]">"The majority of retailers don't know how much engagement their post-checkout messages get."</p>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-[var(--ink-muted)]">-- Julian Krenge, CTO, parcelLab</p>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-heading text-[var(--ink)] mt-12 mb-4">Key Takeaway 3: Co-Creation Over Roadmaps</h2>
        <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
          The company prioritizes customer collaboration over predetermined roadmaps. This approach ensures features address actual customer needs rather than generic development timelines.
        </p>

        <div class="my-10 rounded-2xl bg-[var(--surface-sunken)] p-8">
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.1em] text-[var(--ink-muted)]">On Product Development</p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-lg font-medium text-[var(--ink)]">"I have a personal aversion against roadmaps... we value co-creation."</p>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-[var(--ink-muted)]">-- Julian Krenge, CTO, parcelLab</p>
        </div>

        <div class="my-12 border-t border-[var(--line)]"></div>

        <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
          The podcast provides a deep dive into how parcelLab approaches the supply chain challenge from a technology perspective, offering practical insights for retailers looking to transform their post-purchase operations.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <InnerPageCTA />
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
